import React from 'react';
import { Flex, Box, Image, Button, Heading } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import money from '../images/money.png'; // using images with import


function HomePage() {
    return(
        <Box h="100%" m="0">
          <Box  
          background="linear-gradient(135deg, #D86FCC 0%, #01055B 100%)"
          borderRadius="45px 45px 300px 45px"
          color="white"
          display='flex'
          m="auto"
          w="85%"
          h="455px"
          p="70px"
          // justifyContent="center"
          >
            <Flex direction='column' align="flex-start" justify="center" mr="200px">
              <Heading as='h1' size='xl' mb="15px">
                  Track your payments, balances, and dues between groups
              </Heading>
              <Button mt="15px" bg='#CA41D6' size='lg' _hover={{ bg: '#e261ed' }}>Get Started</Button> 
            </Flex>
          
            <Flex align="center" mr="100px">
              <Image width="400px" src={money}/>
            </Flex>
        </Box>


          <Box
          bg="#2B3699"
          w="100%"
          mt='25px'
          display="flex"
          flex-flow="column"
          h="100%"
          flex="1 1 auto"
          >
            hello world
          </Box>
        </Box>
        
    );
} 


export default HomePage;
